quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  97,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  97,1,hum ne iss ( quran ) ko shab qader mein nazil kya hai
  97,2,aur tum kya jano ke shab qader kya hai ?
  97,3,shab qader hazaar mahino se ziyada behtar hai
  97,4,farishtay aur rooh uss mein apne Rab ke azan se har hukum le kar utartay hain
  97,5,woh raat sara sar salamti hai tulu Fajar taq
